high_descs: Walk straight and enter into the right side room. Then turn left to reach the tv stand
Take the spatula from the tv stand
Turn back and walk straight and take a left turn and walk straight to reach a bowl which is kept on the dining table
Put the spatula in the bowl
Take the bowl along with spatula
Turn left walk few steps and again take a right turn and walk out of the room. Turn right immediately to enter into the bathroom and reach the sink by walking straight
Put the bowl along with spatula in the sink
